node.text:
In ‘Fashionscapes,’ @ecoage founder @liviafirth digs deep into the impact of diamond mining in Botswana—discovering how the industry emphasizes long-term investment in community, environmental sustainability, and empowers women at all levels.⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣
To learn more, watch the full film on IGTV & visit the link in bio.⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣
#NaturalDiamonds #RealisRare⁣⁣⁣

node.text: Diamond jewelry knows no gender and these pieces are proof. 💎 Gender-free jewelry goes beyond trend, but we've seen a surge in unisex pieces this year and we're obsessed. Where would you wear this diamond dog tag? Link in bio for more!

node.text: To Celebrate #WorldElephantDay🐘, we're taking a deeper look at how @debeersgroup is working to protect these amazing creatures through the Moving Giants program, where elephants are translocated to help the species thrive all over Africa. Think you know your elephant facts? Head to our stories for a fun quiz then tap the link in bio to learn more.
